          <div style="display:inline-block; background:#FFF8E6; color:#F39C12; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:20px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:16px;">⚡ The Alert</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:26px; font-weight:800; color:#1B4965; margin-bottom:12px; line-height:1.3;">PostureTru detects your slouch instantly. A gentle vibration reminds you</h3>
          <p style="font-size:16px; color:#666; line-height:1.7;">The moment your back bends past 25 degrees, the smart sensor activates. A subtle vibration — not annoying, just enough — brings your awareness back to your posture without breaking your flow.</p>
