          <div style="display:inline-block; background:#EDFAF3; color:#5FB878; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:20px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:16px;">✅ The Result</div>
