          <a href="/products/posturetru" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:24px; background:#1B4965; color:white; padding:14px 32px; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:16px; text-decoration:none;">Get PostureTru — 50% OFF Today</a>
